thread.title: Cal’s Sonny Dykes named to Dodd Trophy Watch List
thread.title_full: Cal’s Sonny Dykes named to Dodd Trophy Watch List - San Francisco Chronicle

author: Connor Letourneau
title: Cal’s Sonny Dykes named to Dodd Trophy Watch List
text:
Photo: Rick Bowmer / Associated Press California head coach Sonny Dykes looks on in the second half during an NCAA college football game against Utah Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, in Salt Lake City. Utah won 30-24. (AP Photo/Rick Bowmer) California head coach Sonny Dykes looks on in the second half...
Sonny Dykes has been one of 20 coaches named to the mid-season watch list for the Dodd Trophy, officials from the Bobby Dodd Coach of the Year Foundation and Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl announced Friday in a news release.
